{"id":113,"date":"2023-11-15T17:31:42","date_gmt":"2023-11-15T09:31:42","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/120.26.217.177\/?page_id=113"},"modified":"2024-01-30T16:49:18","modified_gmt":"2024-01-30T08:49:18","slug":"research","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/index.php\/research\/","title":{"rendered":"Research"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Topics<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\"><strong>1. Topological Quantum Computing<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n<p>Designing platforms and strategies towards topological quantum computing by demonstrating non-Abelian statistics through Majorana fusion and braiding\u00a0<\/p>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"843\" src=\"https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/topological_quantum_computing-1024x843.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-358\" style=\"width:515px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/topological_quantum_computing-1024x843.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/topological_quantum_computing-300x247.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/topological_quantum_computing-768x633.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/topological_quantum_computing.jpg 1185w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n<p>Related Publications: T. Zhou et al., <a href=\"https:\/\/www.nature.com\/articles\/s41467-022-29463-6\">Nat. Commun. 13, 1738 (2022)<\/a>; T. Zhou et al., <a href=\"https:\/\/journals.aps.org\/prl\/abstract\/10.1103\/PhysRevLett.125.157402\">Phys. Rev. Lett. 124, 137001 (2020)<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\"><strong>2. Topological Transport<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n<p>Quantum states in topological insulators, semimetals, and superconductors, along with their interactions with external fields, such as forces, heat, light, electricity, magnetism, etc. Quantum transport behavior in the superconductor-semiconductor interface, such as Andreev reflection, Josephson effect, superconducting diode effect, etc.<\/p>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"503\" height=\"262\" src=\"http:\/\/120.26.217.177\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/topological_transport.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-330\" style=\"width:724px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/topological_transport.png 503w, https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/topological_transport-300x156.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 503px) 100vw, 503px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p>Related Publications: T. Zhou et al., <a href=\"https:\/\/journals.aps.org\/prl\/abstract\/10.1103\/PhysRevLett.127.116402\">Phys. Rev. Lett. 127, 116402 (2021)<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\"><strong>3. Topological Response<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n<p>The intriguing properties of quantum materials, such as novel electronic structure, superconductivity, magnetoelectricity, optics, transport, etc. It also involves the design and prediction of materials with specific functionalities.<\/p>\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"938\" height=\"1024\" src=\"http:\/\/120.26.217.177\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/topological_response-1-938x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-338\" style=\"width:575px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/topological_response-1-938x1024.jpg 938w, https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/topological_response-1-275x300.jpg 275w, https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/topological_response-1-768x838.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/topological_response-1.jpg 963w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 938px) 100vw, 938px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n<p>Related Publications: G. Xu, T. Zhou*, et al <a href=\"https:\/\/journals.aps.org\/prl\/abstract\/10.1103\/PhysRevLett.124.137001\">Phys. Rev. Lett. 125, 157402 (2020)<\/a>; T. Zhou* et al <a href=\"https:\/\/www.nature.com\/articles\/s41563-022-01466-0\">Nat. Mater. 22, 284 (2023)<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Methods development<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"http:\/\/120.26.217.177\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/methods-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-334\" style=\"width:1029px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/methods-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/methods-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/methods-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/methods-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/methods.jpg 1961w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Topics 1. Topological Quantum Computing Designing platf &#8230; <a title=\"Research\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/index.php\/research\/\" aria-label=\"\u7ee7\u7eed\u9605\u8bfbResearch\">\u9605\u8bfb\u66f4\u591a<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/113"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=113"}],"version-history":[{"count":21,"href":"https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/113\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":524,"href":"https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/113\/revisions\/524"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.zhouphy.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=113"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}